--Add the following code to your controller script, under the System slot and inside the flush() filter. Find a suitable line anywhere below the Final Inputs but above the Engine Commands, and not interfering with other code structures.

--AutoBrake
if unit.getThrottle() < 5 then
   if math.abs(vec3(core.getWorldVelocity()).x) + math.abs(vec3(core.getWorldVelocity()).y) < 20 then
       finalBrakeInput = 1
   end
end
